{"tid":877780,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"17月大男嬰需麻醉　公院錯誤注射多9倍「K仔」氯胺酮　一度留醫ICU","createTime":"2018-10-26T15:20:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-27T07:53:54.000Z","uid":79563,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"d52a6dfd541aabb6017e24d44eb50f742da0af7d","tid":877780,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T15:20:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20181026/s00001/e85b35d0bbe5f45b0a8081d5190922fb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20181026%2Fs00001%2Fe85b35d0bbe5f45b0a8081d5190922fb.jpg&h=c45e8805&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n醫管局周五（26日）出版新一期《風險通報》，當中指出一名17個月大男嬰，為接受腎臟掃描而接受麻醉時，被錯誤注射多9倍俗稱「K仔」的氯胺酮麻醉藥。男嬰一度血氧下跌，要送往兒科深切治療部（PICU）留醫，幸最終回復清醒及無併發症。事件被列為「重要風險事件」。<br />\n<br />\n醫管局指，該男嬰因腎積水及腎盂輸尿管連接部梗阻（ureteropelvic junction obstruction），入住涉事公立醫院接受腎掃描。他先後接受兩種鎮靜藥物麻醉均無效，醫生B應召到場，口頭指示為男嬰注射氯胺酮作麻醉。<br />\n<br />\n醫生A將每毫升液體含50毫克氯胺酮的藥物，錯誤當成是每10毫升液體才含50毫克氯胺酮，並口頭指示護示準備5毫升有關藥物。結果原應接受0.5毫升藥物、共25毫克氯胺酮注射的男嬰，被注射了250毫克氯胺酮，涉事針筒則標示為「25毫克氯胺酮」。<br />\n<br />\n男嬰其後血氧含量下跌，醫生B覆檢氯胺酮濃度時發現錯誤。醫護人員放棄為男嬰進行腎臟掃描，並將他轉送兒科深切治療部留醫。他其後逐漸回復清醒，沒有併發症。<br />\n<br />\n今期《風險通報》另臚列公立醫院在今年4至6月呈報的另外9宗「重要風險事件」，包括9宗藥物事件及一宗誤辨識病人身分事件。公院同期另呈報4宗「醫療風險警示事件」，包括一宗手術後遺留醫療物料在病人體內個案、兩宗住院病人自殺個案，及一宗在錯誤部位施行程序個案。"},{"pid":"ed7f89820bd22fe937b84dc819de2da31e83b1a2","tid":877780,"uid":47112,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T15:33:22.000Z","msg":"high 爆"},{"pid":"de18e5c0d83c814b94cb078bbd435a70cf71b062","tid":877780,"uid":70786,"like":86,"dislike":0,"score":86,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T15:44:18.000Z","msg":"BB high high high<br />\n屌你公院正仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b388c5f1dad62b12efdf50916e275f9b622152f8","tid":877780,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T16:01:22.000Z","msg":"窮人生仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c27df0bfd19725ecbc2441af7baad07768ce822c","tid":877780,"uid":176166,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T16:20:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cb0d009453cd322dbb11564c6340951ef01f6423","tid":877780,"uid":5489,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T16:23:42.000Z","msg":"茄 你個b索茄"},{"pid":"9fcc61ea9a7edfb2aeccac38cd0e9abd51ce8a85","tid":877780,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T17:08:38.000Z","msg":"點解又俾理由輸入大陸醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab29e752b41b0426e22cc5cd5d7d4deb8def5870","tid":877780,"uid":113183,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T17:10:47.000Z","msg":"公院越來越垃圾<br />\n有命入都唔知有無命出"},{"pid":"3612777014084cca998fc41292f871e43ddc0087","tid":877780,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T17:15:59.000Z","msg":"冰茄曲香"},{"pid":"8fbad70a178a535325814095f4efd663c26f9156","tid":877780,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T17:21:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>醫生A將每毫升液體含50毫克氯胺酮的藥物，錯誤當成是每10毫升液體才含50毫克氯胺酮，並口頭指示護示準備5毫升有關藥物。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n依家仲話要降低醫學院收生要求<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9aa9f7d1a6b81c329d718783961e76a30b7d4b17","tid":877780,"uid":2404,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T17:27:22.000Z","msg":"咁細個就吸毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"806b01bf16344f590cea49e43caa1bb302260f84","tid":877780,"uid":89514,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T18:44:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"